    readTime: "9 min read",
    image: "/images/blog6.jpg"
  },
  // Add more posts with specific categories like 'PO', 'Clerk', 'NTPC', 'Railways', 'Class 10'
  {
    title: "Strategy for IBPS PO Prelims",
    excerpt: "Detailed guide to crack the IBPS PO preliminary examination.",
    date: "June 1, 2023",
    category: "PO",
    readTime: "7 min read",
    image: "/images/blog7.jpg" // Placeholder image
  },
  {
    title: "How to Prepare for SSC CGL Quantitative Aptitude",
    excerpt: "Tips and tricks for mastering the quantitative section of SSC CGL.",
